{"tid":1785611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（罷工第二彈）（多謝社福手足）社福界罷工活動","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T07:35:15.000Z","uid":307414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd290e842cc79688ce59ffbf7d14fa2989ff57a","tid":1785611,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"話說琴日愛丁堡其實係有社福罷工造勢大會<br />\n但基於和你shop既post係哂熱門，令熱門無一個post係支持社福界手足罷工<br />\n大家要知道三罷已經悄悄進行緊，唔同界別既工會相繼成立 唔同界別（如白領，酒店業）都相繼有街站招攬唔同人。（詳情請睇三罷tg: hkonstrike)<br />\n今次社福界手足大罷工，係繼廣告界手足後既第二彈，相信社工係呢場運動行得幾前唔洗同大家講，不停幫被捕人士拎名，甚至之前陳虹秀社工被告暴動等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDMyfYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDMyfYi.jpg&h=c6fb4c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而聽日將會有五區社福界既手足集會並且已獲批不反對，無論係咪社福界既手足，都應該全力支持佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝社福手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">組織工會，全面罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n幫P牌推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5fe3cb80f0d1ff954a11793dbf0a1935615e08","tid":1785611,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於明日主題為哀悼 請各位穿黑衫到場以示哀悼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1U75uD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg